Follow this workflow for all NEW components and/or blocks

1. Create a task list to manage component workflow ([task-list.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/task-list.mdc))
2. Think about the current design system and sample a few existing components for inspiration
3. Implement the component defintion ([components.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/components.mdc))
4. Write a story for the component with histoire (follow rules in [stories.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/stories.mdc) and sample a few existing stories for inspiration)
5. Write documentation for the component (follow rules in [docs.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/docs.mdc) and sample a few existing docs for inspiration)
